  "title": "\"Yasubije amahoro mu rugo rwacu\" - Alice M.",
  "summary": "Iyi nkuru ya Alice M. igaragaza urugendo rukomeye rw’umuntu wahanganye n’ibibazo bikomeye mu rugo rwe, aho habagaho kutumvikana, amakimbirane n’ubwumvikane buke byatumaga urugo rutagira amahoro n’ituze. Ni urugendo rugaragaza ukuntu ubuzima bushobora kuba bugoye ariko bukongera guhinduka binyuze mu cyizere.\n\nAlice yatangiye kubona ko ibintu bitagenda neza mu rugo rwe, ariko aho gushaka amakosa ku bandi, yahisemo gutangira guhinduka ubwe mbere.\n\nYatangiye gusenga, gutekereza no gushaka uburyo bwiza bwo kuvugana n’abandi bo mu rugo rwe mu mahoro.\n\nBuhoro buhoro, imvugo ye yarahindutse, imyitwarire ye itangira kuba myiza, bituma n’abandi batangira kumva impinduka.\n\nIbi byatumye imibanire itangira koroha, amakimbirane agabanuka, urukundo rutangira kugaruka.\n\nAbagize umuryango batangiye kuganira neza, kubabarirana no kubaka amahoro mashya.\n\nUrugo rwahindutse ahantu heza ho kuba, huzuye urukundo n’ubwumvikane.\n\nAlice yaje gusobanukirwa ko impinduka zitangirira ku muntu ku giti cye.\n\nUbu atanga ubuhamya bwe nk’isomo ku miryango iri mu bibazo hirya no hino.\n\nInkuru ye ni ikimenyetso cy’uko amahoro ashoboka igihe abantu bahisemo guhinduka.",
